OL,7,FMedia watchdog Ofcom has written to ITV
OL,8,Fand Sky "to ask them to explain their
OL,9,Factions" after the family of Nicola
OL,10,FBulley claimed they had been contacted
OL,11,Fby the broadcasters after asking for
OL,12,Fprivacy following the discovery of her
OL,13,Fbody.
