OL,16,Ffamily through Lancashire Police after
OL,17,Fthe missing 45-year-old's body was
OL,18,Ffound in the River Wyre, singled out
OL,19,Fthe broadcasters as having made contact
OL,20,Fwith them directly after they had
OL,21,F"expressly" requested privacy.
